{"id": 2198, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都见过或者不自觉地用过哪些“战斗语言”？", "description": "即，一种以言过其实、夸张蛮横为特点的富有时代气息的语言风格，它们至今也没完全从我们的表达习惯里淡去。", "record_count": 1708, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201802261650196myBxpVo7ReGKbHh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-27T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 267776, "content": "生于忧患 死于安乐啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1161604}, {"id": 268800, "content": "吃饭不积极，脑子有问题?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279008}, {"id": 268545, "content": "我高中班主任经常说，撸起袖子加油干??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276522}, {"id": 267522, "content": "我们要用感恩的心某某", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222469}, {"id": 267268, "content": "表决心时说做好了准备“全面决战”、“打好一场硬仗”", "image": null, "praise_count": 118, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 267524, "content": "夺取全面建成小康社会的伟大胜利！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272671}, {"id": 268036, "content": "你瞅啥？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273035}, {"id": 267269, "content": "反省自己也常常要“消灭”自己的不足和缺点", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 267525, "content": "努力工作努力学习！(其实也就说说而已)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853433}, {"id": 267270, "content": "表示全力支持时就忍不住“不惜一切代价”", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 268038, "content": "撸起袖子就是干", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274745}, {"id": 267784, "content": "起立！\n老师好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273955}, {"id": 267529, "content": "好好学习，考上大学就轻松了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258939}, {"id": 267785, "content": "起立！\n老师好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273955}, {"id": 267530, "content": "不要怂，就是干。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001171}, {"id": 267531, "content": "扑领母", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272717}, {"id": 267532, "content": "我们现在处于并将长期处于xx主义社会初级阶段", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 267533, "content": "你们所有的努力都是为了高考！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272723}, {"id": 267534, "content": "今晚早睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251301}, {"id": 271118, "content": "打爆你的狗头", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289459}, {"id": 267535, "content": "军训的时候大喊 能打胜仗 作风优良", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619263}, {"id": 267537, "content": "这回答牛头不对马嘴，果然完全不懂的人还是多数啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194904}, {"id": 267539, "content": "“向我开炮”\n“革命尚未成功，同志仍需努力”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624578}, {"id": 267542, "content": "风萧萧兮易水寒……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272762}, {"id": 268310, "content": "不不，你没有理解我的意思，我的意思是.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276287}, {"id": 268312, "content": "一分一操场", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251032}, {"id": 267546, "content": "You did it!", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272777}, {"id": 267547, "content": "铁肩担道义！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256752}, {"id": 267548, "content": "我能，我行", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258933}, {"id": 267549, "content": "我能，我行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258933}, {"id": 267550, "content": "别把世界让给你讨厌的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272361}, {"id": 267551, "content": "撸起袖子加油干", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272785}, {"id": 267554, "content": "富强民主文明和谐公正法治爱国敬业诚信友善", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272792}, {"id": 267555, "content": "突破，改善，创新", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272793}, {"id": 268323, "content": "骚年 莫方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225207}, {"id": 267813, "content": "感恩，感恩，感恩！！！！\n感你妹。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236729}, {"id": 268325, "content": "f……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089878}, {"id": 267558, "content": "不说了，就是干", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974517}, {"id": 267559, "content": "弱国无外交 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753653}, {"id": 267815, "content": "虽然说生活需要激情，可是日复一日的过着差不多的日子也是很心累的_(:з」∠)_，偶尔也丧一丧吧……丧个十分钟就行……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265233}, {"id": 267560, "content": "感觉回答都好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088651}, {"id": 268072, "content": "打着工作旗号，各种人身攻击道德绑架。以敬业加班之名，行偷懒赚钱之实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140901}, {"id": 267561, "content": "那好吧，那就不好意思了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104222}, {"id": 267563, "content": "上了大学就好了，就没人管你了\n爱怎么疯就怎么疯吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272835}, {"id": 267564, "content": "不考研不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259391}, {"id": 267565, "content": "最常说的一句“加油！你是最棒的！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649889}, {"id": 267567, "content": "砥砺奋进", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897636}, {"id": 267568, "content": "不同意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115782}, {"id": 267569, "content": "从来没有一夜成名，只有百炼成钢", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272239}, {"id": 268338, "content": "他还是个孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276685}]}